  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Burn patients treated in an outpatient clinic and ICU survivors are at risk of malnutrition.&#xD;
      There are no clear guidelines determining the energy target in those two populations. The aim&#xD;
      of this observation study is to measure the resting energy expenditure of those patients,&#xD;
      using indirect calorimetry.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
